name: &6The Fossil Thief
author: Matty
description: Dr Trayaurus' fossil was stolen by a Thief. Help him get it back!
location: Talk to Dr Trayaurus at the Casino!

Dialog.&d&lDr Trayaurus: Help [PLAYER]!!!
I've been robbed!
I need your help!
Earlier today I went to the Casino to have some fun with my friends.
We were having a great time playing BlackJack.
We all put some valuables as a wager which the winner of the game would then take.
After about 3 hours I had finally won the game!
I was so happy that I won and that I will be able to keep all the items.
My best friend &c&lMatt &rput something very valuable to him as the wager.
It was his 1 of a kind Fossil.
After all... We are all scientists.
He handed the Fossil to me and I decided to leave.
Playing 3 hours straight of blackjack was tiring.
I started going home when suddenly...
A Thief jumped out of no where.
He stole the 1 of a kind Fossil!
Then he ran off before I could catch him.
I need your help getting it back!
Dialog.[PLAYER]: Sure thing! Of course I will help.
Do you have any idea where he went?
Dialog.&d&lDr Trayaurus: Yes, um...
I am pretty sure he ran toward the cave!
Be careful though...
There are a bunch of Miners in there.

Dialog.[PLAYER]: Hey, can I ask you a quick question?
Have you seen anyone unusual come in this cave?
Possibly carrying a bag? With a Special Fossil?
Dialog.&7&lMiner: No, not that I know of...
Although, their was this one guy who ran into the cave.
I think he tripped and fell and ran back out though.
Oh! And he had a bag!
I am pretty sure our Lead Miner put his bag somewhere in the cave since he left it.
Sadly, I couldn't tell you where it is though or which it is...
You can come back tomorrow and ask him if you want.
Dialog.[PLAYER]: No, but what if another Miner takes the bag home!
Then I will never get the Fossil back!
Dialog.&7&lMiner: I mean, you can look through all our bags if you want.

Objective: Search the Bags for the Special Fossil
SendMessage: &8[&6&l!&8] &7To Search the Bags you &6Stand &7on them or &6Right-Click&7 on them!

Dialog.[PLAYER]: Yes! I finally found it!

Objective: Head over the Bridge back to Dr Trayaurus

Dialog.&8&lThief: Where do you think you're going?
You ain't just going to take that Fossil that easily...
Thanks for finding it for me...
I lost it when I tripped in the cave.
Dialog.[PLAYER]: Yeah, I know... I heard all about it.
Nice job! You couldn't even make a easy getaway...

Dialog.&8&lThief: If you want it then you'll have to fight me!
Dialog.[PLAYER]: I'll do anything for Dr Trayaurus!
Come at Me!!!

NpcBattle.&8&lThief: You thought it would be that easy?
You haven't seen the end of me.
Well, would you look at that.
The fossil is going to be mine forever!

Dialog.&8&lThief: If I can't have this fossil then no one can!

Dialog.[PLAYER]: Dr Trayaurus! I had it...
I found it in the cave.
But then, the Thief was waiting outside the cave.
I beat him yet he wouldn't give it up!
He crushed it into pieces...
What do I do now?
Dialog.&d&lDr Trayaurus: [PLAYER], If you collect all the pieces of the fossil, I can use &6Pok Power &rto restore it!
Hurry, make sure you collect all the pieces.
I'll be by the front entrance when you return!

Objective: Head to the front of the Casino to give the Fragmants to Dr Trayaurus

Dialog.&d&lDr Trayaurus: Great work! This looks like all of them.
Did you hear that?
Dialog.[PLAYER]: Yeah!
Dialog.&d&lDr Trayaurus: You should go check it out.
I'll be waiting here.

Objective: Stop the fight between Todd and Billy

Dialog.[PLAYER]: Guys. Calm down!
How about we settle this the right way.
I battle both of you and if I win you guys are banned from the Casino.
Well... You arn't banned from the Casino then.
Now Separate!

NpcBattle.&7&lTodd: Oh wow. I was not expecting that.
I'll give you a retry whenever you want.

NpcBattle.&7&lBilly: Wow... You have some nice Pokmon!
I knew you could never beat me...
Battle me again when you think you can beat me!

Dialog.[PLAYER]: So I won...
Now I guess you both are banned.
What were you guys fighting over in the first place?
Dialog.&7&lTodd: I did not. I swear he left it somewhere.
Dialog.[PLAYER]: Well did you check around?
Wow... Then I will check.
So...
What do you have to say to Todd.
No...
How about you go home for the day.
Seems you are a little on the edge.
And for you...
Well, you did nothing wrong so I guess you can stay.
Dialog.&7&lTodd: Thank you so much! I think a theif came in here and hid his money.
Dialog.[PLAYER]: Well, I wouldn't be suprised. I have to go back to helping Dr Trayaurus now.
He has a urgent project, we are working on restoring a Fossil!
Dialog.&7&lTodd: Oh, thanks! Good luck with that.

Dialog.&d&lDr Trayaurus: Nice Work, [PLAYER].
You really are a friendly &cPokmon &rplayer.
Dialog.[PLAYER]: Wow. Thanks!
Dialog.&d&lDr Trayaurus: Which reminds me!
You can friend people by doing &e/friend [name]
Dialog.[PLAYER]: Oh wow! That is cool.
Dialog.&d&lDr Trayaurus: Its a super cool way to see when your friends are on and create friends through playing &cPokmon&r!
Well anyways... Back to the Restoration!
Now in order to restore the fossil we need &e&l &eElectricity Rods &e&l&r!
Dialog.[PLAYER]: What are &e&l &eElectricity Rods &e&l &rand where can they be found?
Dialog.&d&lDr Trayaurus: They can be found all around the Casino.
They are filled with Electricity, they will have enough energy to power our restoration process.
We need 4 &e&l &eElectricity Rods &e&l &rtotal!
Dialog.[PLAYER]: Okay, I am on it.

Objective: Return the Electricity Rods to Dr Trayaurus

Dialog.&d&lDr Trayaurus: Great work! Now I need 4 &eMagnemites&r.
&eMagnemites &rare super good for this project.
They can withstand the high amounts of energy from the Electricity Rods and transmit it onto the fossil fragmants.
Nice one! Tell me when you are ready.
Dialog.[PLAYER]: Im ready when you are!
Dialog.&d&lDr Trayaurus: Okay. Lets stand back.
Here goes nothing!

Objective: Pickup the Fossil that was restored!

Dialog.&d&lDr Trayaurus: It worked!
I think you deserve to keep it.
You helped me so much with getting it back from them.
You are the true hero.
Dialog.[PLAYER]: No no, its yours.

Objective: Talk to Dr Trayaurus more about the Fossil

Dialog.&d&lDr Trayaurus: You can keep it!
Unless you want to battle for it?
Dialog.[PLAYER]: Sure!
Dialog.&d&lDr Trayaurus: Great. Winner gets it!

NpcBattle.&d&lDr Trayaurus: I guess you'll be keeping the Fossil.
I can't take the fossil from you.
Battle me again when you think you can beat me!

Dialog.&d&lDr Trayaurus: Say... Would you be down to trade it for a Pokmon!
Dialog.[PLAYER]: Sure! What kind of Pokmon?
Dialog.&d&lDr Trayaurus: Fossil Pokmon!
Dialog.[PLAYER]: Oh wow! I would love to trade it!
Dialog.&d&lDr Trayaurus: Great, let me take you over to select one!
Choose your Fossil Pokmon!
Great Choice!
Here, let me give you some goodies as full repayment!
Dialog.[PLAYER]: Wow! Thanks so much.
Dialog.&d&lDr Trayaurus: Well, I have to go now!
